'''Lady''' was a title and also a respectful form of address. "[[Lord]]" was a typically [[Gender|masculine]] equivalent of "lady."

==History==
The [[planet]] [[Mustafar]] was home to Lady [[Corvax]].<ref name="ImmortalI">{{VaderImmortal|I}}</ref> [[Padmé Amidala]] was referred to as "my lady" or "milady," though she was the [[Monarch of Naboo|Queen of Naboo]] and later [[senator]] for her people.<ref name="TPM" /><ref name="AOTC">{{Film|II}}</ref> Lady [[Bo-Katan Kryze]] was the [[regent]] of [[Mandalore]] following the [[death]] of her sister, [[Duchess]] [[Satine Kryze|Satine]], during the [[Clone Wars]].<ref name="Heroes of Mandalore" /> Towards the end of the war, the [[Sith Lord]] [[Maul]], who split from his [[Darth Sidious|master]] and attempted to lead the criminal underworld through syndicates such as the [[Shadow Collective]] and [[Crimson Dawn]], intended to kill the [[Jedi]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker]] at the [[Siege of Mandalore]]. When Skywalker's former [[Padawan]] [[Ahsoka Tano]] confronted Maul instead, the renegade Sith disparagingly mocked his adversary's lack of an official rank, calling her "Lady Tano."<ref name="TPA">{{TCW|The Phantom Apprentice}}</ref> The ancient Jedi droid [[Huyang]] later referred to Ahsoka Tano as "Lady Tano" when aiding on her quest to find [[Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo|Thrawn]]. The [[mercenary]] [[Baylan Skoll]] referred to his employer, the [[witch]] [[Morgan Elsbeth]], as "Lady Morgan."<ref name="Part One">{{Ahsoka|Part One: Master and Apprentice}}</ref> Being of royal bloodline, Senator [[Carise Sindian]] of [[Arkanis]] was addressed by the title of Lady on various occasions, although she was deprived of this honor after [[Leia Skywalker Organa Solo|Leia Organa]] arranged for Sindian to be stripped of her noble status with the [[Elder Houses]] in retaliation for the actions that Carise had perpetrated against both Organa and her friend, [[Ransolm Casterfo]].<ref name="Bloodline">[[Bloodline (novel)|''Bloodline'']]</ref>

During the [[War of the Bounty Hunters]], the [[Galactic Empire]]'s ally, [[Tagge Corporation]], was led by Lady [[Domina Tagge]],<ref name="Tagge">[[Doctor Aphra (2020) 6|''Doctor Aphra'' (2020) 6]]</ref> while the Crimson Dawn syndicate was led by Lady [[Qi'ra]].<ref name="WotBH 1">[[War of the Bounty Hunters 1|''War of the Bounty Hunters'' 1]]</ref> [[Landonis Balthazar Calrissian|Lando Calrissian's]] yacht was named the ''[[Lady Luck]]''.<ref name="Last Shot">''[[Last Shot]]''</ref>

